</code></pre></div><p>The binary allows us to allocate a small chunk between <code>0x1f</code> and <code>0x38</code> bytes:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-c" data-lang="c"><span style="color:#66d9ef">int</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">small_alloc</span>()
