</code></pre></div><p>If we reach <code>[1]</code>, <code>alloc_array[2 * idx]</code> is freed leading to a double free.</p>
<p>We can print a chunk only once:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-c" data-lang="c"><span style="color:#66d9ef">int</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">examine</span>()
