</code></pre></div><p>Finally we can malloc a huge chunk, but we cannot write anything within:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-c" data-lang="c"><span style="color:#66d9ef">int</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">savebig</span>()
